r other TV channels will bring your company a higher profitability.<br />\nAs one of the most popular brands in Hong Kong, has become part of our daily life. In the darkest times, we sincerely hope that you will stand with HongKongers to fight for freedom and democracy.  We, as loyal customers, herewith plead your company to halt advertisement on TVB and to reject any TVB advertisement offer.  Please request your HK distributor, Kaeru Pharmaceutical HK Ltd to stop employ TVB and it artist as brand ambrassor.<br />\nBeing an international company but at the same time a locally renowned brand, we wish to see you to stand with HongKongers.<br />\n<br />\nYours sincerely,<br />\nXXX"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"Reference#1<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Li_Ruigang\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FLi_Ruigang&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=eed1a03c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Li_Ruigang</a><br />\n<br />\nReference#2<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/solomonyue/status/1191591144205012992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolomonyue%2Fstatus%2F1191591144205012992&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=83164c5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolomonyue%2Fstatus%2F1191591144205012992&h=87e6ed5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/solomonyue/status/1191591144205012992</a><br />\n<br />\nReference#3<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-include-television-broadcasts-limited-tvb-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-include-television-broadcasts-limited-tvb-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=aTFRN7Q3AKWWv%2B0RVwuGmkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=f69a498c\" data-auto-link target